message.text:
Hello guys! Meet Tiger🐯
(Ako nag name hehe)

Dog siya around FEU TECH na paligoy ligoy and super bait. You can pet tiger if kilala ka na nya hehe. Not sure if may owner pero 1 week ko na siya nakikita here.

Rating nya sa siomai 10/10
Rating sa kwekkwek 4/10

Ayun reminder lang to be kind sa doggies 🐶

Hello guys! Meet Tiger🐯
(Ako nag name hehe)

Dog siya around FEU TECH na paligoy ligoy and super bait. You can pet tiger if kilala ka na nya hehe. Not sure if may owner pero 1 week ko na siya nakikita here.

Rating nya sa siomai 10/10
Rating sa kwekkwek 4/10

Ayun reminder lang to be kind sa doggies 🐶
